SecurityLabelDisable=true

Then restart:

systemctl --user daemon-reload
systemctl --user reset-failed gitlab-runner
systemctl --user restart gitlab-runner
sleep 10
systemctl --user status gitlab-runner --no-pager -l

Why this is happening

There were two separate issues:

Issue 1:
Podman tried to process the image-defined /home/gitlab-runner volume.
Fix:
--image-volume=ignore
Issue 2:
GitLab Runner then tried to chdir into /home/gitlab-runner.
But the container user could not access your bind-mounted host directory.
Likely fix:
Use :U on the /home/gitlab-runner bind mount.

