Phase 9 — Update converge.yml

Use include_role instead of a static roles: block:

---
- name: Converge
  hosts: all
  gather_facts: true
  become: "{{ lookup('env', 'AEROLIT_BECOME') | default('true', true) | bool }}"
  tasks:
    - name: Run role under test
      ansible.builtin.include_role:
        name: "{{ lookup('env', 'ROLE_NAME') }}"

This gives you more control later when you need conditions, variables, debug, or role wrapping.

